<div class="tool-panel guide-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>怎么选参数</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="guide-grid">
    <div>
      <strong>中心频点</strong>
      <p>填你要处理的频点。找共振点时先扫频大致定位，再微调。修改此值会联动更新左右频点。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>Q</strong>
      <p>Q 决定滤波器带宽。越大范围越窄（精准处理），越小范围越宽（整体调节）。常用取值 0.7~4。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>左右频点</strong>
      <p>左频点为低频边界，右频点为高频边界。填左右频点后工具会自动反算中心频点和 Q。两种方式双向联动，用哪种都行。</p>
    </div>
    <div>
      <strong>增益</strong>
      <p>正值为提升，负值为衰减。建议每次只调 1~3 dB，优先用窄带（高 Q）处理谐振峰。</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel preset-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>场景预设</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="preset-row" aria-label="EQ 参数预设">
    <button type="button" data-eq-preset="broad">宽带修正</button>
    <button type="button" data-eq-preset="notch">窄带削峰</button>
    <button type="button" data-eq-preset="vocal">人声存在感</button>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="split-fields three">
  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="eq-center-input">中心频点 (Hz)</label>
    <input id="eq-center-input" inputmode="decimal" value="1000" data-eq-input="center" />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="eq-q-input">Q</label>
    <input id="eq-q-input" inputmode="decimal" value="1.414" data-eq-input="q" />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="eq-gain-input">增益 (dB)</label>
    <input id="eq-gain-input" inputmode="decimal" value="6" data-eq-input="gain" />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="split-fields">
  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="eq-left-input">左频点 (Hz)</label>
    <input id="eq-left-input" inputmode="decimal" value="707.071" data-eq-input="left" />
  </div>

  <div class="tool-panel compact-panel">
    <label class="field-label" for="eq-right-input">右频点 (Hz)</label>
    <input id="eq-right-input" inputmode="decimal" value="1414.285" data-eq-input="right" />
  </div>
</div>

<div class="status-line" data-status data-state="ok">
  <span aria-hidden="true">●</span>
  <span>等待处理</span>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel result-panel">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2>结果抄写表</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="result-grid">
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>Center</span>
      <strong data-eq-result="center">-</strong>
      <em>中心频点</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>Q</span>
      <strong data-eq-result="q">-</strong>
      <em>滤波器带宽参数</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>Bandwidth</span>
      <strong data-eq-result="bandwidth">-</strong>
      <em>左右频点差值</em>
    </div>
    <div class="result-row">
      <span>Octaves</span>
      <strong data-eq-result="octaves">-</strong>
      <em>带宽对应倍频程</em>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel">
  <canvas class="eq-canvas" id="eq-canvas" width="960" height="420" aria-label="EQ 曲线"></canvas>
</div>

<div class="tool-panel">
  <label class="field-label" for="eq-output">输出</label>
  <textarea id="eq-output" readonly spellcheck="false" placeholder="计算结果会显示在这里"></textarea>
</div>
